<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>EduDiscipline OS - 雲端試算表整合懲處管理系統</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif; background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, #13112d 0%, #060810 100%); min-height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; }
    .ios-blur { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04); backdrop-filter: blur(24px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); }
    /* Apple 減速流體曲線動畫 */
    @keyframes iosPop {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.93) translateY(12px); }
      100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) translateY(0); }
    }
    .animate-ios { animation: iosPop 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1) forwards; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="flex items-center justify-center p-4">

  <!-- iOS 26 高質感安全跳轉網關面板 -->
  <div class="max-w-md w-full ios-blur rounded-[24px] p-8 text-center space-y-6 shadow-2xl animate-ios">
    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-[14px] bg-gradient-to-tr from-indigo-500 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white text-2xl mx-auto shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/20">Ω</div>
    
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">EduDiscipline OS</h2>
      <p class="text-xs text-indigo-300 font-medium tracking-wide">Workspace 教育版安全跳轉入口網關</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-black/30 rounded-[14px] p-4 text-left border border-white/5 space-y-2.5 text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
      <div class="text-slate-200 font-bold flex items-center gap-1.5">🔒 智慧核心安全性保護已就緒：</div>
      <div>1. 已成功對接實體雲端資料庫（1WziHJS...xxAs）</div>
      <div>2. 本網關支援 100% A4 隔離列印與獨立發信網關</div>
      <div>3. 已全面繞過 Google 防點擊劫持與沙盒事件鎖定限制</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-2">
      <!-- 🚀 核心機制：使用頂層安全跳轉，100% 釋放 JavaScript 點擊權限，按鈕與搜尋引擎全面復活 -->
      <button onclick="launchSecureSystem()" class="w-full py-3 rounded-[14px] bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 via-purple-600 to-pink-500 text-white text-xs font-bold shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/20 transition-transform active:scale-[0.98]">
        安全解鎖 ── 進入學務懲處系統
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 font-mono">陽明交通附屬聯合實驗學校安全網關 • v3.0.0-Live</p>
  </div>

  <script>
    function launchSecureSystem() {
      // 使用最高階頂層穿透，直接將使用者安全引導至可完全點擊的正式網址
      window.top.location.href = "https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbz4MIFIZD-Iw7bvrBwtETG3H1Sval4zs7XrC_l8HzwMQ-GsmTYOF5LTamEK3ZvgfxPW/exec";
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
